675
00:35:42,820 --> 00:35:45,342
Farò il possibile.

676
00:35:46,762 --> 00:35:48,643
A me deve andare adesso.

677
00:35:57,652 --> 00:36:01,695
Tenimelo fermato, mi raccomando.

678
00:36:01,715 --> 00:36:02,115
D'accordo.

679
00:36:03,416 --> 00:36:04,938
Respira.

680
00:36:05,579 --> 00:36:05,840
Ok.

681
00:36:06,519 --> 00:36:11,764
Tira sullo schienale.

682
00:36:26,427 --> 00:36:26,947
A tre.

683
00:36:27,289 --> 00:36:29,769
Uno, due, tre.

684
00:36:29,929 --> 00:36:31,170
Ok, vai a prendere ossigeno.

685
00:36:31,269 --> 00:36:33,010
Dai ragazzi, muoversi.

686
00:36:33,090 --> 00:36:34,871
Dai, dai, dai, dai.

687
00:36:34,911 --> 00:36:35,791
Signor Caracci, vi riconosce?

688
00:36:35,811 --> 00:36:37,253
Legatura dei tre atti, rapidi.

689
00:36:58,148 --> 00:36:58,648
L'altro braccio.

690
00:36:58,668 --> 00:36:59,108
Sta collassando.

691
00:36:59,128 --> 00:36:59,989
Defibrilliamo, via.

692
00:37:00,070 --> 00:37:00,250
Su.

693
00:37:00,489 --> 00:37:01,570
La maglietta, Cini.

694
00:37:01,690 --> 00:37:02,771
Via io, via noi, via tutti.

695
00:37:02,791 --> 00:37:03,231
Libera.

696
00:38:00,168 --> 00:38:02,891
